author: marrs
msg: ACE-107 Added a login dialog that pops up over the main ACE UI and forces you to log in. You can use the default used called "d" with password "f" to log in, or configure different users in UserAdmin (you have to provide a credential called "password" so you can login. Other ways of authenticating are currently not supported.
